1. Hero Section
Components: Image + Title + Subtitle + CTA Button
Content:
Title: “Création de Landing Pages Personnalisées”
Subtitle: “Offrez à Votre Entreprise une Présence en Ligne Impactante”
CTA Button: “Contactez-nous pour un Devis Gratuit”
Visuals: A high-impact image that represents professionalism and online success.



2. Why Choose a Landing Page?

Components: Icon List or Accordion
Content:
Short intro explaining the benefits: “Une landing page dédiée est essentielle pour…”
Key Points (icon list or accordion items):
Présenter votre offre de manière claire et attractive.
Améliorer votre visibilité en ligne et renforcer votre image de marque.
Générer des leads qualifiés grâce à des appels à l’action efficaces.
Visuals: Small icons for each point to make the list visually engaging and easy to read.

3. Our Services

Components: Section with Image + Card for Each Offering
Content: Three cards summarizing each main offering (Design, User Experience, Performance).
Card 1: Design Moderne et Personnalisé
Short Description: “Layouts professionnels et identité visuelle cohérente.”
Card 2: Expérience Utilisateur Optimale
Short Description: “Responsive design et navigation intuitive.”
Card 3: Performance et Rapidité
Short Description: “Chargement ultra-rapide et optimisation des médias.”
Visuals: Each card can include a relevant icon or mini-image to make it stand out.

4. Technology and Packages

Components: Table for Package Comparison
Content: Use a comparison table for Standard and Premium packages.
Columns: Feature, Standard (WordPress), Premium (Custom Framework)
Rows/Features:
Platform: WordPress / Custom Framework (Astro.js, Tailwind CSS)
Pages Included: 1 / 4
Design: Professional design / Unique design
Contact Form: Basic / Advanced options
Performance Optimization: Yes / Ultra-fast code optimization
CTA Below Table: “Demandez un Devis Gratuit”
Visuals: Table format for quick comparison.


6. How to Choose the Right Package?

Components: Card Grid or Icon List
Content:
Card 1: Pack Standard
“Idéal pour une présence en ligne rapide et simple.”
Card 2: Pack Premium
“Parfait pour ceux qui recherchent un design unique avec plusieurs pages.”
Card 3: Pack Sur Mesure
“Pour les besoins complexes et l’accompagnement complet.”
Visuals: Cards with icons or checkmarks to illustrate why each package suits different needs.

7. Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

Components: Accordion
Content: FAQ items that answer common concerns.
Example Questions:
Combien de temps faut-il pour créer une landing page ?
Puis-je modifier le contenu moi-même ?
Proposez-vous l'hébergement et le nom de domaine ?
Visuals: Expanding accordions for easy reading without clutter.

8. Client Testimonials (Optional)

Components: Testimonial Cards
Content: Short testimonials or reviews to add social proof.
Example: “DigiDevs nous a aidés à obtenir une page efficace et élégante, parfaite pour notre image de marque.”
Visuals: Cards with client names, images, and brief quotes.

9. Footer with Contact Information

Components: Footer Links, Contact Info Section, Social Media Icons
Content:
Contact Information:
Email: contact@votreentreprise.com
Phone: +33 6 12 34 56 78
Link to contact form: “Contactez-nous”
Visuals: Clean footer with all necessary contact details and links to social media.
Suggested Subcomponents:
Hero Section: Use an image background with overlay text and a clear CTA button.
Icon List: Simple list with icons to represent each key feature.
Cards: For summarizing offerings and benefits with short descriptions.
Comparison Table: For displaying feature differences between packages.
Accordion: To expand each package’s detailed features and FAQ answers.
Testimonial Cards: Optional cards with a client quote and image.
Footer Links and Contact Info: Contact information at the bottom with social links.
